    title: "Stop Rebuilding Storyboards: Convert Word to SCORM Faster",
    description: "Discover how to streamline your rapid e-learning workflow by using AI responsibly and converting approved Word storyboards directly into SCORM packages.",
    excerpt: "The real bottleneck in rapid e-learning isn't writing â€” it's rebuilding. Learn how to use AI at the right stages and turn your approved Word storyboard directly into a deployable SCORM package.",
    publishAt: "2026-05-05T09:00:00-03:00",
